{"tid":1484890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係跪喺度求你地","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:36.000Z","uid":16086,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6671a443e7a91144e32e8ebe079893a66808a9ac","tid":1484890,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"快啲散啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係勇武 之前都企前排<br />\n<br />\n不過今日真係和理非日<br />\n<br />\n之前和理非咁支持我地<br />\n<br />\n我地都支持翻佢地<br />\n<br />\n返屋企好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過埋今日林鄭唔回應<br />\n<br />\n我地去中環個山上面發夢<br />\n<br />\n唔洗今日搞住嘅"},{"pid":"d94751205947371fecda241fdc591c56faed8e06","tid":1484890,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"淋完雨好返屋企沖涼喇<br />\n現場手足如果勸完都唔走就自己走啦，佢地見冇人都會走<br />\n<br />\n停止捉鬼，由得啲鬼自己OT啦"},{"pid":"bdb66134abeffae186a049ff2f3a409681e274d0","tid":1484890,"uid":64031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"你點可能叫到啲鬼走<br />\n啲鬼未收到上面 order<br />\n係唔可以走的"},{"pid":"3e87e59c72a75f8c9bdf5eefc530e01a005833d8","tid":1484890,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"我已經走左 因為以身作則<br />\n<br />\n我希望手足都會快啲離開<br />\n<br />\n雖然 最後有咩事都唔會同你地割席<br />\n<br />\n你地都有自己決定<br />\n<br />\n但係我都想絶最後努力勸你哋"},{"pid":"76a5a4001fb87e5e0a85e69833592d0aef083b84","tid":1484890,"uid":296170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n求大家立即散<br />\n求下你地<br />\n咁黑警下次冇得不發不反對通知書</span></span>"},{"pid":"74d585c5a9593e717d439c35f221ff944a558fd5","tid":1484890,"uid":142803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"走啦"},{"pid":"f711a616cb2326958a5c87433cd291e0a151de18","tid":1484890,"uid":297357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>求大家番屋企休息喇</strong></span>"},{"pid":"385ec7726997cb1a58dcff77b9bfc79010645d38","tid":1484890,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"現場唔走嘅都係警犬扮"},{"pid":"b3f5e5da47dd32665c7f14d7f80fd9fda16be029","tid":1484890,"uid":289850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界<br />\n返屋企</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c2b258d74452c68f7439ebe91f0ea4b0d7a4587","tid":1484890,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"我有朋友喺現場<br />\n<br />\n佢未走<br />\n<br />\n但係問佢做咩<br />\n<br />\n其實又冇咩做"},{"pid":"c19af1585e538a073776e08cfe43e9c3e5373c86","tid":1484890,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:01.000Z","msg":"求下大家<br />\n行完就返屋企啦好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次咪當係和理非主埸俾下面<br />\n話哂今次都咁多人出黎，咁姐係證明大家都無離棄到勇武啦係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果今次和理非大成功政府都唔回應<br />\n咁大家再勇武都出師有名啦係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家今次返屋企啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"5f9dbde32be19ad16d1a53eecabda1592e90672b","tid":1484890,"uid":292739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"和理非要有上前的勇氣<br />\n勇武也要有退後的胸襟<br />\n<br />\n和理勇武，本是同根。"},{"pid":"d8d7ce5d4c7c95e25c454dd02698e7b18e7959cf","tid":1484890,"uid":75648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d36e2e21c6de37d88ea1170efa2b686665bafc65","tid":1484890,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係金鍾既人可唔可以唔好咁自私 <br />\n早啲返屋企唔得 係都要踩死線 出哂防暴個啲先叫有做野？<br />\n個個都要擔驚受怕咁睇撚住你地 坐係到唔知做乜撚 次撚次都係咁 出左防暴 聽日個焦點又轉移左 可唔可以比返日個焦點係和理非到 今日咁多人出黎淋雨既努力 可唔可以唔好因為坐多個幾十分鍾而白費 求下你地啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"38914c1850e00b86e8294b075ce0427c0984c33d","tid":1484890,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f2c2170cc11ddd9e548838adb068da809de8af5","tid":1484890,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d2bc7b71bcbda9325031cba105a1f15fb2faf1c","tid":1484890,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"我語氣好好<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以真誠傾下<br />\n<br />\n點解要留金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52914ff659f294781789410961ec66e767fb47f","tid":1484890,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"邊個唔肯返屋企就係鬼!<br />\n<br />\n去咗金鐘嘅手足快D返屋企啦!<br />\n<br />\n聽日玩特襲好過啦!機場好，接公務員放工又好，總之宜家唔好留喺金鐘啦!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32240c89b56a2d13f8e4f0faa193e8a60e8afe13","tid":1484890,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e52914ff659f294781789410961ec66e767fb47f","tid":1484890,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"邊個唔肯返屋企就係鬼!<br />\n<br />\n去咗